text.tspan: Change in commodity price index of cereal crops and petroleum,
Global commodity price index of cereal crops and petroleum, measured relative to real prices in 1900 (where 1900 = 100).
Source: Jacks, D.S. (2019), "From Boom to Bust: A Typology of Real Commodity Prices in the Long Run." Cliometrica 13(2), 202-220.
